specified using ``n``.  Optionally also with ``delta``. Alternatively the range
of expected occurences can be specified by ``min`` and/or ``max``.

$attribute_list::5
]]>
      </xs:documentation>
    </xs:annotation>
    <xs:attribute name="expression" type="xs:string" use="required">
