(e.g. ``format="interval"``). See
[/config/datatypes_conf.xml.sample](https://github.com/galaxyproject/galaxy/blob/dev/config/datatypes_conf.xml.sample)
for a list of supported formats.</xs:documentation>
      </xs:annotation>
